{"tid":521284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【會唔會狂投訴R著數？】華航降落一刻 商務艙天花板跌落嚟險傷客","createTime":"2018-01-06T11:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T11:42:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"072d49ef8c9d934dc997ed7b91da380af8e0cc33","tid":521284,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57674607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57674607&d=Jfrr3VwRFbLVwLPZ0c4nXAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=24daa192\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57674607&h=670a8e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57674607</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515237315_2e42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515237315_2e42.jpg&h=65356e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐商務客位差點「中頭獎」？有台灣旅客投訴，昨日（4日）乘坐華航CI-522廣州飛桃園航班，降落時商務艙的天花板突然掉落，差點擊傷周圍旅客。<br />\n<br />\n華航表示，1月4日CI522廣州-桃園航班，商務艙前側部份天花板於飛機降落時鬆脫掉落於通道上，空服員於第一時間確認無旅客及機組人員受傷。該航機於旅客下機後隨即執行全面檢測，完成修復，初步排除飛行安全疑慮，原因將交由波音公司原廠檢測，這是華航的波音747飛機發生天花板突然鬆脫掉落首宗案例，對於驚動旅客，華航深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"9ba2c1e9b7b39abb1d21a3a6c7696a93ad3cbe16","tid":521284,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"差點擊中，即係無擊中啦"}]}